Package: accel-exporter
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: accel-ppp
Description: Prometheus exporter for Accel-PPP
 A Prometheus exporter for Accel-PPP that exposes metrics from the
 'accel-cmd show stat' command. The exporter collects various metrics
 including general system metrics, core metrics, session metrics,
 PPPoE metrics, and RADIUS metrics with server labels.
 .
 Features:
  * Exposes all metrics from accel-cmd show stat
  * Configurable listen address and metrics path
  * Ready-to-use Grafana dashboard
  * Docker support